data.description: Sellers have made a massive price improvement! This is your opportunity to purchase a 2-story 4 bedroom home on a cul-de-sac in the Village Green neighborhood! This home offers 4 bedrooms, a full basement and fenced in back yard. Home updates include: New carpet installed January 27, 2024, HVAC 2019, water heater 2022, whole home water softener 2016, roof 2015. Enjoy an easy commute with quick access to SR 104, SR 33 and I-270. Walking distance to Three Creeks Metro Park with dog park, athletic fields, playgrounds, fishing, canoe/kayak access and walking trails. Less than a 10 minute drive to the grocery store, library and restaurants.
